<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Semistrict consensus tree of two trees inferred from 28 SrDNA sequence data aligned by secondary structure, one the majority rule tree using Bayesian methods and the other the unique tree produced using maximum parsimony. Bayesian analysis runtime = 2 million generations (25 % burnin). Branch support: Bayesian posterior probabilities / symmetric resampling (1,000 replicates). (-) indicates branch support below 0.5 / 50." , "Figure 4. Neothlipsis agathoides a Lateral habitus of a melanic specimen b Lateral habitus of a pale specimen c Dorsal habitus d Fore wing, arrow pointing to second submarginal vein." , "Figure 3. Neothlipsis parysae a Lateral head and mesosoma b Dorsal head and thorax c Dorsal propodeum and metasomal terga 1 - 3 d Wings." , "Figure 2. Neothlipsis parysae a Lateral habitus b Dorsal habitus." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11307" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11310" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11309" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11308" .

